OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FA man from Leeds has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fencouraging an American's suicide
OL,8,Fduring a video call.
OL,10,FDylan Phelan, 21, goaded Travis Dyer
OL,11,Finto shooting himself in October 2024
OL,12,Fas the pair spoke on the online
OL,13,Fplatform Discord.
OL,15,FMr Dyer, 21, from Louisiana in
OL,16,FAmerica, was known to be vulnerable
OL,17,Fand struggling with his mental health
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
