PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FAt Leeds Crown Court on Wednesday,
OL,7,FPhelan pleaded guilty to encouraging
OL,8,Fsuicide.
OL,10,FHe had already admitted possessing
OL,11,Findecent and extreme images.
OL,13,FPhelan was released on conditional
OL,14,Fbailed to be sentenced on 22 May.
OL,16,FThe judge told him: "Prepare yourself
OL,17,Ffor custody".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
