FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fsaid Phelan attended Elland Road
OL,8,FPolice Station in Leeds with his
OL,9,Fparents in March last year to report
OL,10,Fhis involvement in Mr Dyer's death.
OL,12,FHe disclosed he had taken part in a
OL,13,Fvideo call, with two others based in
OL,14,FAmerica, during which Mr Dyer was
OL,15,Fencouraged to take his own life with a
OL,16,Fshotgun, which he did while the video
OL,17,Fcall was ongoing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
