PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FA police investigation revealed Mr
OL,7,FDyer was subjected to sustained and
OL,8,Fserious encouragement to self-harm by
OL,9,Fmembers of the online group.
OL,11,FIn his police interview, Phelan said
OL,12,Fhe had become "drawn to the darker
OL,13,Fgroups" on Discord and "accepted his
OL,14,Fwords were a factor in the suicide".
OL,16,FPolice also found an indecent image of
OL,17,Fa child and other extreme pornography
OL,18,Fimages on Phelan's devices.
OL,20,F'Travie, we miss you'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
