CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FMr Dyer lost his mother and younger
OL,7,Fsister in a car crash, 10 years before
OL,8,Fhis own death.
OL,10,FA tribute posted by his great-
OL,11,Fgrandmother said: "Travie, we miss
OL,12,Fyou. Needless to say, I'm so beside
OL,13,Fmyself. I don't know what to say or
OL,14,Fhow to say it.
OL,16,F"Sweetheart, you were so unfortunate
OL,17,Fto have had so many tragedies in your
OL,18,Fyoung life. It was totally unfair for
OL,19,Fyou."
OL,26,@sD@SOUxD@AOU{D@EO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
