PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,FAlex Johnson, senior prosecutor for
OL,7,Fthe CPS said: "This was a deeply
OL,8,Fdisturbing case involving the
OL,9,Fexploitation of a vulnerable young man
OL,10,Fthrough an online platform.
OL,12,F"Dylan Phelan did not merely witness
OL,13,Fwhat happened ` he actively
OL,14,Fparticipated in goading Travis Dyer to
OL,15,Ftake his own life, intending that he
OL,16,Fwould do so.
OL,26,@oD@OOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
