PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773252369
OL,3,CMan admits encouraging American to
OL,4,Cshoot himself on live video call
OL,6,F"Online spaces are not beyond the
OL,7,Freach of the law. Encouraging self-
OL,8,Fharm or suicide, whether in person or
OL,9,Fthrough digital platforms, is a
OL,10,Fserious criminal offence.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with Travis
OL,13,FDyer's family and friends. We hope
OL,14,Fthat today's conviction brings them
OL,15,Fsome measure of justice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@YO]
